<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- mā ạảb̊hay̱ ạản̊ naj̊tamiʿa
 ḥaẘla ạl̊ḥabībi lil̊madīḥ̊
 waḥubũnā ḥubuⁿ̃ ṣarīḥ̊
 waqaṣ̊dunā maj̊du ạl̊masīḥ̊

[C1]
   ạlqrạr: maj̊daⁿạ liman̊ tanāzala
   ḥatãy̱ yunīra ạl̊maḥ̊fala
   maj̊daⁿạ liman̊ fī was̊ṭinā
   maj̊daⁿạ lisākini ạl̊ʿulạa

[V2]
 2- hadẖā surūru ạlậbi ạản̊
 naq̊ṣida daẘmaⁿạ maj̊dahu
 hadẖā surūru ạlậbi ạản̊
 naray̱ yasūʿa waḥ̊dahu

[V3]
 3- was̊ṭa ạlạảḥibãạ yaḥ̊ḍuru
 biạl̊barakāti yā̊̉muru
 taʿ̊zīaẗuⁿ fāyỉḍaẗuⁿ
 min̊ jūdihi tan̊hamiru

[V4]
 4- fah̊wa ḥabībunā ạl̊gẖanī̃
 wamin̊ gẖināhu nagẖ̊tanī
 wāl̊qal̊bu min̊hu yam̊talī
 wāl̊ʿaẘna min̊hu nar̊tajī</lyrics>
<title>mạ ạ̉bhy̱ ạ̉n njtmʿ ḥwl ạlḥbyb llmdyḥ</title>
</song>